# Enclosure Notes

## Suggested V1 enclosure dimensions

```text
Outer size: 70 mm x 115 mm x 22 mm
PCB size: 60 mm x 100 mm
Wall thickness: 2 mm
Screws: M2 or M2.5
```

## Mechanical layout

- OLED window near top/front.
- 5 button holes under OLED.
- USB-C cutout on bottom edge.
- Battery pocket on back side.
- Antenna area must remain plastic only.
- Avoid metal screws directly beside antenna area.

## Beginner-friendly enclosure style

Use a simple two-piece screw enclosure first. Snap-fit designs look cleaner but are harder to tune.

